collectionMetadata.name: List of NEA Licensed Eating Establishments with Grades, Demerit Points and Suspension History
collectionMetadata.description:
List of NEA licensed eating establishments with grades and track records.
The demerit points and suspension history is based on past 1 year.
You may also visit the NEA website (http://www.nea.gov.sg/public-health/food-hygiene/nea-food-establishment-licensees)” for the “List of NEA Licensed Caterers with Grades, Demerit Points and Suspension History”
